name: Simon-Lennert Raesch
body:
# About
Lennert is working at the [Software Engineering Research Group](seblog.cs.uni-kassel.de) at [Kassel University](www.uni-kassel.de) where he is currently focussing on graph transformation tools for game development and development of VR applications.

# Published Projects
+ **Comet Tail** on the [iOS App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/app/comet-tail/id1068440823)
+ **Babylon.One** on the [iOS App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/app/babylon.one/id935001053), [Google Play Store](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tv.babylonone.application)
+ **About Love, Hate and the other ones** on the [iOS App Store](http://itunes.apple.com/app/about-love-hate-other-ones/id558459510)

# Contact
